app的话应该是看开发者想怎么做，技术上来说程序也可以是马上完全停止，也可以在退出界面一直在后台跑着，顶多就是有可能会触发操作系统弹出权限要求的提示<br />
举个例子前一阵子美国优步就发过公告说他们准备设置成用户下车后继续在后台收集5分钟的地理位置<br />
<br />
<br />
基于基站的历史定位的话根据以前披露出来的信息当时美国NSA已经做到了在全球定位数以亿计的手机<br />
The National Security Agency is gathering nearly 5 billion records a day on the whereabouts of cellphones around the world, according to top-secret documents and interviews with U.S. intelligence officials, enabling the agency to track the movements of individuals — and map their relationships — in ways that would have been previously unimaginable.<br />
<br />
The records feed a vast database that stores information about the locations of at least hundreds of millions of devices, according to the officials and the documents, which were provided by former NSA contractor Edward Snowden. New projects created to analyze that data have provided the intelligence community with what amounts to a mass surveillance tool.<br />
<br />
其实现在存储很便宜，之前看什么文章说过，一个用来记录下来全美几各类通信信息的数据中心花费也就15亿美金，情报部门肯定是把所有能看到的东西统统存下来再说				<p class="author">
